data.Caption: I’m so happy to be getting old with you.
You’re aging like a fine wine.
You’re not aging — you’re leveling up!
Life should not only be lived, it should be celebrated. Happy birthday.
I am so freakin happy you were born.
Happy birthday to one of the few people whose birthday I can remember without a Facebook reminder.
Birthdays come around every year, but friends like you only come once in a lifetime.
Surround yourself with people who are more excited for your birthday than you are.
Living young and wild and free.— Snoop Dogg and Wiz Khalifa
Friends are the family we choose for ourselves. Happy birthday!
No treasure compares to the love of a brother. Wishing you a wonderful birthday, dear brother.
Though even the sun will one day run out of fuel, my love for you shall last forever. Happy Birthday, dear brother.
Doughnut crush my sister's vibes on her birthday.
